text:
Hare Krishna! Prabhu ji
Aapse ye jo positive vibes aati h na inhe aise hi rakhna inhi k sahare first sem easy hua tha. Us time p aapse baat krke aise dil halka ho jata tha, thanks a looooot for that time. baaki to bhot saari memories abhi bnani h aapke saath Iff duniya ki moh maya se uthke aap himalayas na chle jaye. udhar b vse hum aapko chhordenge nhi.

text:

text: ye to sabko pta h tu most humble, hardworking, mast chitrkar, mast libero, mast whistler h. lekin bhot kum logo hi pta h ki tu kitna accha vlogger b h. Umeed krta hu ki tere bhot saare vlogs dekh pau.

text:
YO KAR!!
Tumhare bina padhayi karna bhot mushkil ho jata. or vo exams ki padhayi k beech m hi ekdum pubg khelna start kr dena. tumne jo 100 rs. m spotify diya tha usme abhi b gaane download nhi ho rhe h. "aree chuna laga gya" . Bhai prayas m tumne bhot mehnat ki h aise hi acche acche kaam krte rhna. or campus wapas na aane k liye daily meri taraf se ek gaali apne liye maan lena. jaldi milte h.
